features.text:
# Lala Gallery of Crypto Art (North), Helios Island

Event: First CNFT Exhibition April 18 - May 9, 2021

| Floor        |Conent    |
| ----------- |:---------:|
| Ground        | CNFT Exhibition Spacebudz      |
| First        | CNFT Exhibition Cardanobits, Berry NFTs  |
| Second         | Permanent Collection     |
| Third         | Rooftop and Pool     |

# Spacebudz

Creators Ale and Zieg released the Spacebudz in March 2021. In the pre-sale there was a rocket launch on the website. The distribution was automatic and random. 10000 unique pieces, varying in rarity, from dinos, bulls, frogs, elephants, cats, dogs and more.

# Cardanobits

Creator Francisco released the Cardanobits in March 2021. 
The pre-release was a bit of a fun and wild ride to remember, using Google Docs, crashing the Yoroi Wallet and more. 10000 pieces, varying in rarity, from zombies, aliens, shadows, humans and more.

# Berry NFTs

SPO Ale, co-founder of Spacebudz, minted some berries on the day of the Mary hard fork in March 2021. 100 different colors of berries for the first 100 delegators of his pool.

# Welcome!

You are at Lala Gallery of Crypto Art.

Great to have you here. Enjoy your stay!

Let's stay connected, see the icons below.

xoxo Lala

The first NFT collection minted on the Cardano Blockchain. Each one different in color, representing the diversity in the Cardano community and given for free to the first 100 Berry Stakepool delegators

# Words of Berries in the Cardano Field

* Berry Vermilion: “Simply brilliant from Ancient Rome, the Middle Ages, the Renaissance to the present day.”

* Berry Lust: “The look, the name, it’s all the same.”

* Berry Melanie: “You left me speechless.”

* Berry Platinum: “A piece of Cardano history. A privilege to hold.”

* Berry Orange: “Orange stands for vitality, enthusiasm and life. This journey is like a fresh juice in the summer sun. We have only just begun.”

* Berry Roux: “How do you pronounce roux one asks? Simple pronunciation, I say … ‘Community’, Roux is a binding agent, a color with as much utility as flair, words that best describe the Cardano spirit.”

* Berry Awesome: “Awesome? Getting most of the lawn work done while the two little girls played in the yard all day.”

 Berry Indigo: "Freedom."

* Berry Azul: “Vers l’infini, et plus loin encore!”

* Berry Pear: “Being an early adopter sometimes feels like a punch in the stomach, but it is still incredibly rewarding nonetheless.”

* Berry Ruby: “If you want to go quickly, go alone. If you want to go far, go together.” 

* Berry Teal: “Unconditional one.”


   Berry Raven: "Some sort of grey."

 Berry Scarlett and Family Tree.

Featured Spacebudz: #8963, #9940, #3214, #0, #9649, #7495, #8963, #9940, #3214, #1403, #6309, #6626, #6834, #9668, #516, #4588, #3911, #6238, #2479, #7579, #1666, #631

Featured Cardanobits: #8010, #1511, #1277, #3837, #8522, #66, #6888, #1939, #1958, #8108, #5088, #1133, #1285, #7243, #9871, #3381, #7501, #624, #6834, #5957, #5826

Featured Berries: Vermilion, Lust, Melanie, Platinum, Orange, Roux, Awesome, Indigo, Azul, Pear, Ruby, Teal, Raven, Scarlett and family.
